# The reviewer test vault ships .daftari/config.yaml and a curated tensions.md
# as part of the bundled fixture. Negate the broad ignores above so they are
# tracked. Database files, the process lock, and the curation log stay ignored.
!templates/reviewer-vault/.daftari/config.yaml
!templates/reviewer-vault/.daftari/tensions.md

